{"tid":1640301,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"依家既政府既弱點係咩！？","createTime":"2019-10-09T02:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T16:39:58.000Z","uid":61520,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"168914a9a2bfdf3512b038edf0e97d0ec51ec9e2","tid":1640301,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:06:40.000Z","msg":"係冇公信力！！！所以呢個政府講咩都好，都會受人質疑！！所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣要focus係緊急法帶來既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&ldquo;經濟危機&rdquo;</span></strong>，市民就會buy！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之前幾單新聞：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n1）中國向香港借4000億美元唔還，滙控CEO辭職<br />\n2）8月份香港銀行的港元存款總額急跌1,110億元<br />\n3）8月本港零售銷貨總值按年大跌23%<br />\n4）近日atm排長龍，甚至冇錢<br />\n5）逾一成ATM受損不能運作，中資銀行成為示威者目標</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢的都係&ldquo;經濟危機&rdquo;既先兆！！<br />\n政府緊急法會令行政機關有無限權利，市民既財產隨時被凍結、沒收，而且政治前景未明，《緊急法》恐嚇走外資，令香港玩完。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只要廣大既市民認為信心危機，要提領現金換美金保平安</span>, 大量市民走去禁錢，會引發更多人去禁錢，透過小道消息將依件事傳出去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地呢個禮拜做d咩，就係要廣泛文宣帶出一個信息，同全香港人講，同全世界講，政府緊急法即將引爆經濟危機，係焦土既選擇，後患無窮，大家可能要適當處理自己的資產！！<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">同埋將五大訴求同經濟復甦掛勾</span></span>，有左普選制度，香港係一個更公開，更公平既自治地方，大家就會有信心投資！大家唔好比緊急法嚇到，被政府帶風向，大家focus太多係蒙面法，私了，裝修，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個緊急法既經濟炸彈大家要識得用！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"875149119529368ebbe49086083f300262789289","tid":1640301,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:08:02.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6286b4a4036063182c9a84fc2cd82fd014572720","tid":1640301,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:08:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n港共春袋係金融體系<br />\n繼續㩒atm make noise 各大傳媒淡化處理呢d事 其實幫緊港共維穩<br />\n銀行call loan 引發支爆 中共到時就會投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>."},{"pid":"91912832fe9e6b23dc67621afb3f0b7925006ce9","tid":1640301,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"加強文宣！<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"296d14244160b2bd5b1718f248a4f44344a1ba68","tid":1640301,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6286b4a4036063182c9a84fc2cd82fd014572720","tid":1640301,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:08:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n港共春袋係金融體系<br />\n繼續㩒atm make noise 各大傳媒淡化處理呢d事 其實幫緊港共維穩<br />\n銀行call loan 引發支爆 中共到時就會投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:28:17.000Z","msg":"個人比較悲觀，依個中国唔會咁易就收皮<br />\n但係我地keep 住排隊禁錢係可以make noise<br />\n令更多人意識到緊急法帶來既危機<br />\n<br />\n至於引發點樣既效果，我地之後就會知"},{"pid":"dd885780d5abee2f656350f44c406702c4ba228d","tid":1640301,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:44:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8a84aa1577505303e0e110e73ee627dbdcbb580","tid":1640301,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7b1f59a15414beb2ff112cab7fb0d8b12e7b789e","tid":1640301,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:46:36.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a72f018b5d53e2edf1d36d45ab4ea56a291cc3","tid":1640301,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:47:20.000Z","msg":"係反政府人仕既團結"},{"pid":"500da15e44a0d43f58691cb7224969ded5ae0bd8","tid":1640301,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a922f850b053fe079f3a18f1cb5789ffa9ea84e","tid":1640301,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4114e2088e9f7fcd6cd57441303a695a9249a05a","tid":1640301,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"星期五中環快閃 撐被捕保安<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7wpcSZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7wpcSZ.jpg&h=a1dc48db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D95Jtrk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-sr